<li id="cite_note-WuChia2015-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-WuChia2015_39-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFJiang_WuLucille_Chia2015" class="citation book cs1">Jiang Wu; Lucille Chia (2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=IX7ICgAAQBAJ"><i>Spreading Buddha's Word in East Asia: The Formation and Transformation of the Chinese Buddhist Canon</i></a>. Columbia University Press. pp.&#160;111–123. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-231-54019-3" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-231-54019-3"><bdi>978-0-231-54019-3</bdi></a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20221020124912/https://books.google.com/books?id=IX7ICgAAQBAJ">Archived</a> from the original on 2022-10-20<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2016-10-20</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Spreading+Buddha%27s+Word+in+East+Asia%3A+The+Formation+and+Transformation+of+the+Chinese+Buddhist+Canon&amp;rft.pages=111-123&amp;rft.pub=Columbia+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-231-54019-3&amp;rft.au=Jiang+Wu&amp;rft.au=Lucille+Chia&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DIX7ICgAAQBAJ&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATripi%E1%B9%ADaka" class="Z3988"></span></span>
